{"tid":1662023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗  願榮光歸香港  之外仲有一首歌","createTime":"2019-10-18T13:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T14:27:43.000Z","uid":141261,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0319208ea3d6071c344bb0a13e78fabd7e8c3cd6","tid":1662023,"uid":141261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:24:41.000Z","msg":"個首就係不屈進行曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n6nm4NKYHDw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn6nm4NKYHDw&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9r2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=a121875d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n6nm4NKYHDw</a><br />\n<br />\n由於實在有太多嘅人臨陣驚得滯向後退， 前線勇武好快就會畀人追到。所以想今次20號一齊唱。尤其是遊行同警方對峙嘅時候唱。<br />\n<br />\n呢首本身dgx巴都話係軍歌，但係都好少人唱，希望20號會聽到，同勇武巴絲同行。"},{"pid":"19b723cf8a26de4a738a93205f2c21d995fe71dc","tid":1662023,"uid":305710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:27:19.000Z","msg":"來同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cc276e1349d373b59830160c9fa7b58c676d4c","tid":1662023,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會唔會太難記1"},{"pid":"613e0dafbe30e99f49539433980525c12ca25fab","tid":1662023,"uid":255884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:32:51.000Z","msg":"每日一定聼一次 幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd85b610aa3faa331daaf259096f5765d2e3bda5","tid":1662023,"uid":141261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56cc276e1349d373b59830160c9fa7b58c676d4c","tid":1662023,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會唔會太難記1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:36:42.000